comments: Lopez (MIL) turns into Randle's (NYK) body and initiates contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) is already in Grimes' (NYK) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Holiday (MIL) is moving alongside Brunson's (NYK) path and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Holiday (MIL) and Brunson (NYK) come together at the same spot and incidental foot to foot contact occurs during the drive.
Holiday (MIL) legally contests Brunson's (NYK) jump shot attempt.
Lopez (MIL) is already in Randle's (NYK) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) is firming up over his right leg and absorbs the contact from Brunson (NYK) to his upper body.
Lopez (MIL) cleanly deflects the ball away from Randle (NYK) during rebounding.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) brings his forearm towards Brunson (NYK) and marginal contact occurs as Antetokounmpo releases away to pursue the rebound.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) is already in Quickley's (NYK) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) and Brunson (NYK) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs off ball.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) places his right hand on Robinson's (NYK) shoulder and restricts Robinson's pursuit of the rebound.
Randle (NYK) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.
Grimes (NYK) contests Holiday's (MIL) jump shot and marginal contact occurs after the release.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) establishes a wide screening position in Grimes' (NYK) path and contact occurs to his leg.
Grimes (NYK) legally contests Holiday's (MIL) jump shot attempt.
Lopez (MIL) legally contests Brunson's (NYK) shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) moves into Brunson's (NYK) path and delivers body contact that affects Brunson's SQBR.
Quickley (NYK) commits a take foul on Allen (MIL).
Fournier (NYK) commits a take foul on Holiday (MIL).
Robinson (NYK) establishes a screening position outside of Holiday's (MIL) field of view, and he gives Holiday a step to avoid the contact.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) is turning away from Brunson's (NYK) path when marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Quickley (NYK) commits a take foul on Allen (MIL).
